{"tid":1383292,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"鬥文宣，我地㩒住政府往死𥚃打。鬥武勇，就調返轉","createTime":"2019-07-29T16:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T01:43:34.000Z","uid":108589,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"98f7f0887a240b7d6d61b517a661d5911f3b9ba6","tid":1383292,"uid":108589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:08:46.000Z","msg":"大家諗返我地每一次鬥文宣，無論登報，動畫影片，連儂牆，樣樣野都係世界級。對面除左整啲白痴，核突到無輪既文宣黎對抗係無晒辦法。我地可以話係贏到開巷。<br />\n但係鬥武勇，只會換黎俾警察做活靶，試練新武器既對象。而且對方係合法打，武力裝備訓練都同我地有天淵之別，佢地係天，我地係地。<br />\n<br />\n所以應該用我地最強既地方去打對方最弱既地方，多用文宣，估宣傳。鬥智，鬥柔性攻擊，我地一定可以爭取到我地要既野。集中火力，要求成立獨立調查委員會徹查勾結黑社會警察，立即推動有意義政改，履行 97 回歸承諾，讓香港市民擁有真正雙普選既權利﹗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4aa19ae072d53eac0d7d6b4c96789570979497e","tid":1383292,"uid":108589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c01904187038e2f7fcd060e4f694a927a606af","tid":1383292,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:16:20.000Z","msg":"既不能力敵就只可智取"},{"pid":"6c9539e9143b0aa5de62ec5259b4d53600c6af74","tid":1383292,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:26:43.000Z","msg":"你又啱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ac9af9602155ebc9d0e8ed50166d4ebfdd20ff","tid":1383292,"uid":270954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:28:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good